Key - Bindings
--------------
Zoom            - ctrl + plus, minus, equel (shift + mouse scroll)
Scollback       - shift + page_up, page_down (mouse scroll)
Copy URL        - alt + y
Open Copied URL - alt + o
Invert Colors   - alt + i

